A4.text: The main event was the 2003 Royal Rumble match, which was won by SmackDown!'s Brock Lesnar

A5.text: At the 2005 Royal Rumble, Cena and Batista were the final two participants and were eliminated simultaneously by one-another. After a restart, Batista won.

A6.text: On January 27, 2013, Cena won his second Royal Rumble match, announcing that he would pursue the WWE Championship at WrestleMania 29.
